snippet.title: ATARASHII GAKKO! - Free Your Mind (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Let go of your inhibitions and free your mind! ATARASHII GAKKO! at full speed! They run around the streets, alleys, and neighborhood shops of Tokyo with skaters in tow as they spread their infectious seishun energy. You gotta dance, you gotta sing, you gotta free your mind!

'SNACKTIME' EP -- out now: https://atarashiigakko.lnk.to/SNACKTIMEID
